heroSubTitle: High school is the connecting bridge with the fulfillment of perspectives and achievements for a good job, a good status and above all a socially prosperous individual that society needs.
missionDesc: Our school, as the first and only high school in Debar, is a school with a long tradition, quality and professional teaching staff, equipped with a new school building, gym, library and classroom teaching with classes gave me. The school provides a safe and secure environment in which it educates, educates and directs the raising of environmental awareness among young people, encourages individuality, creativity and provides a strong foundation for the continuation of higher education institutions. So we prepare young people for learning, training, work and full integration into daily life in a modern, democratic and multicultural country. Our desire is the reputation and appreciation we have built in our city and beyond to maintain and donate it.
